<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA515_02_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema515_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_02_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">
          <div>
            준희는 쓰레기를 오전에
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>13</span>
              <span>20</span>
            </div>
            kg, 오후에
            <div class="fraction_box">
              <span>4</span>
              <span>15</span>
            </div>
            kg 주웠습니다. 준희가 오전과 오후에 주운 쓰레기는 모두 몇 kg인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_40">
          <div class="img_box">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA515_02_IH/0006_img.png" alt="" />
            <div lang="y">
              <span class="color1">환경</span>의 <span class="color2">날</span>
              <span class="color3">체험</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="div flex dir_col gap_40">
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="13"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="20"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="+" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">답</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline">
                <div class="fraction_box mr_10">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field></div>
                </div>
                <span>kg</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <!--start solve-->
                <p lang="y">(준희가 오전과 오후에 주운 쓰레기의 무게)</p>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4 mt_40 mb_30">
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>13</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <span>+</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>4</span>
                    <span>15</span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>39</span>
                    <span>60</span>
                  </div>
                  <span>+</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>16</span>
                    <span>60</span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="slash">55<span class="slash_txt">11</span></span>
                    <span class="slash">60<span class="slash_txt">12</span></span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box mr_2">
                    <span>11</span>
                    <span>12</span>
                  </div>
                  <span> (kg)</span>
                </div>
                <!--/end solve-->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
